title: A Saudi, an Indian and an Iranian walk into a Qatari bar ...
description: Iranian-American comedian Maz Jobrani takes to the TEDxSummit stage in Doha, Qatar to take on serious issues in the Middle East -- like how many kisses to give when saying “Hi,” and what not to say on an American airplane.
author: Maz Jobrani
keywords: TED, talks, Middle East, TEDx, comedy, culture, entertainment, humor, performance
